{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a new premium transparency/trust section for the Calm Nights product page.
    
    
    
    Goal:
    Replace the current sleep-stat section with a short section that explains why Calm Nights is different.
    
    
    
    Add an image option at the top:
    Allow us to upload or insert a picture at the top of the section. Keep it clean, premium, and mobile-friendly.
    
    
    
    Section copy:
    
    
    
    Headline:
    Most Supplement Labels Don’t Tell The Full Story
    
    
    
    Main stat:
    80%
    
    
    
    Stat sentence:
    of herbal supplements tested were mislabeled.¹
    
    
    
    Make the “¹” a small clickable superscript source link. Do not add a separate source line.
    
    
    
    Supporting line:
    Missing ingredients. Unlisted fillers. Labels that didn’t match.
    
    
    
    Turn:
    Calm Nights was built for people who are done guessing.
    
    
    
    Proof line:
    Every dose disclosed. Standardized extracts. No proprietary blends.
    
    
    
    CTA button:
    Shop Calm Nights
    
    
    
    CTA behavior:
    The button should scroll/take the customer back to the top product purchase section.
    
    
    
    Design:
    Make the 80% the biggest visual element in the section. Use a clean white background, Ariya purple accents, centered layout, and mobile-first spacing. Keep the section short, premium, and conversion-focused. Do not over-explain the study, make the 80% have an animation of starting from 0% and reaching 80% when you scroll to it, get rid of this line completely, Every dose disclosed. Standardized extracts. No proprietary blends., could you make under calm nights was built for people who are done guessing, 3 check marks one on the left, one in the middle and one on the right with an option for me to insert text next to the checkmark, could you make the checkmarks aligned with each other in the middle , make the sho calm nights button scroll you to the top of the page when you press it, for the source link put a mini star above the period in mislabeled where i can insert my URL link
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
